calculate changes in peak npp to negative npp for each species and climate. use Day of center of mass - so 50% of it happens before and 50% after

readout_yd <- readout %>% 
  mutate(dyear = ifelse(wy==2011 | wy==2017, "wet", "drought")) %>%
  group_by(yd, climmod, dyear, code) %>%
  summarize_at(vars(gpsn, resp, npp, trans), list(median))

prac <- readout_yd %>% 
  dplyr::filter(climmod=="hist" & code=="quag" & dyear=="wet")

# can just sum it up and find the day
# need to get cumulative npp
gethalf <- function(yd, npp){
  df <- data.frame(npp=npp, yd=yd)
  
  df$sumnpp = cumsum(abs(df$npp))
  last=length(df$npp)
  int = df$sumnpp[last]
  
  halfsum=int/2
  ydhalf = df$yd[df$sumnpp>=halfsum]
  day50 <- ydhalf[1]
  
  return(list(int=int, half=day50))
}

gethalf(yd=prac$yd, npp=prac$npp)
## $int
## [1] 435.6155
## 
## $half
## [1] 147
tmp <- readout_yd %>% group_by(code, climmod, dyear) %>%
  summarise(halfnpp=gethalf(yd=yd, npp=npp)$int,
              ydnpp=gethalf(yd=yd, npp=npp)$half)
## `summarise()` regrouping output by 'code', 'climmod' (override with `.groups` argument)
ggplot(tmp) + geom_point(aes(x=ydnpp, y=halfnpp, col=climmod, shape=dyear)) + facet_grid('code')

tmp2 <- readout %>% 
  mutate(dyear = ifelse(wy==2011 | wy==2017, "wet", "drought")) %>%
  group_by(climmod, dyear, code, run) %>%
  summarise(halfnpp=gethalf(yd=yd, npp=npp)$int,
              ydnpp=gethalf(yd=yd, npp=npp)$half)
## `summarise()` regrouping output by 'climmod', 'dyear', 'code' (override with `.groups` argument)
ggplot(tmp2) + geom_boxplot(aes(x=climmod, y=halfnpp, col=dyear)) + facet_wrap('code') + labs(y="gC/m^2", title="net annual NPP")

ggplot(tmp2) + geom_boxplot(aes(x=climmod, y=ydnpp, col=dyear)) + facet_wrap('code') + labs(y="day of year", title="day when 50% net annual NPP")

tmp_summary <- tmp2 %>% 
  group_by(code, climmod, dyear) %>% 
  summarise(
    medianday = median(ydnpp),
    mediannpp = median(halfnpp),
    highday = quantile(ydnpp, 0.95),
    highnpp = quantile(halfnpp, 0.95),
    lowday = quantile(ydnpp, 0.05),
    lownpp = quantile(halfnpp, 0.05))
## `summarise()` regrouping output by 'code', 'climmod' (override with `.groups` argument)
ggplot(tmp_summary) +
  geom_hline(aes(yintercept=0)) + 
  geom_pointrange(aes(x=medianday, xmin=lowday, xmax=highday, y=mediannpp, ymin=lownpp, ymax=highnpp, col=climmod,  shape=dyear)) +
  facet_grid('code')
